World Cup win
1 intro

Enter Two Fans: 

Fan 1: Bhai saab match ka to maza hi aa gaya kya match hua hai, 10 saal se har bar ekdam last me jaake haarte the aur is baar to last me jaake chakka maar diya

Fan 2: Aisa match maine life me nahin dekha, kya catch liya hai suryakumar yadav ne

Fan 1: Sooryakumar yadav? Samajwaadi se tha kya?

Fan 2: Abe cricket ki baat kra raha hun tu mujhse india k world cup jeetne k agle din ek mahine pahle k election ki baat kar raha hai, tujhe abhi batata hun mai idhar aa

Start fighting: Exit: Khabri throws them away 

2 Khabri News


Khabari - Aa gaye aap log? Ab jahan news milni chahiye wahan milegi nahin to ek chai ke saath ye sab mai hi bata deta hun. Mai hun aapka aapna khabrilal khabardaar



Khabri -  Aaj ki sabse taaja khabar hai ki india ne twenty twenty cricket world cup ko ek baar fir se apne naam kar liya hai poore desh me khushi ki lahar hai.. taaliyaan! 


Team India  mumbai jakar sadkon pe bus ke upar chadhke naachi kyonki aadmi bhale hi kitna bhi bada ho jaye, bus se bada nahi ho sakta! Taaliyan!!! Bajao gaana!

(Khabri dances on Bhangra beat, fans throw money at him and then fight among themselves to catch the same notes they were throwing)

Logon ne Itne patakhe phode ki dilli ka pradushan dar k nepal bhaag gaya, 

10 saal baad bhartiya team ne pehla icc khitaab jeet k duniya ko dikha diya ki pradhanmantri ji panauti nahin hai

Bhartiya team me top two players ki jagah khaali hai aur Shubhman gill ne selection process me apni daawedaari majboot karne ke liye social media par fir se daali tauliye me tasveer.

Kaptaan Rohit aur unki team ne jhanda gaad diya, match jeetne k baad rohit  bhaawuk hokar zameen par chitt gir pade aur poori team unki taraf aise daud padi jaise baraat k saamne kisine noton ki gaddi uda di ho..

 Ye sab dekhte hi mai chai chadhaane bhaag gaya kyonki apna kaam chalte rehna chaahiye. Ye monsoon aur cricket season me jyada chalta hai..

