4 Khiladi Chacha Conversations



Two or Three men enter the set with sawaalin


Man1 : Khiladi chacha pranam, world cup jeetne ki badhai ho!

Chacha: Are hame kya hame koi kahin ek bhi paisa de dega kya? Hamne apne desh k liye khela hame aaj tak ek medal bhi nahin mila.. jeevan bhar ye khabri k baap ke yahan chai peta reh gaya..

Man 1: Are chacha! desh k liye khele the.. kahan khele the one day me ki test me?

Chacha: Ham gali me khela karte the

Man 2: (Laughs) Are chacha aapne gali me hi desh ke liye khel lete the?

Chacha: aur nahin to kya! hamne apni gali me apne desh k liye aisi aisi ladaiyan ladi hain mazal nahi hai ki koi ek se zyada trial ball khel le

Sawaalin: Chacha ab to hamelag raha hai ki jo aap bolte the ki hamaara ek rishtedaar BCCI me hai wo sab bhi jhooth hi tha

Labri: are aaj tak kabhi paan k paise to diye nahin bade aaye BBCI me rishtedaari nikalne waale

Chacha: Tum logon ko sab mazak lagta hai, aajkal k bacche mobile dekh dekh k sochne lage hain ki saari duniya dekh li hai, sab unki umar k logon ne hi ukhaada hai unke bade boodhon ne to kuch dekha hi nahin

Sawaalin: Haan to kahan hain aapke BCCI waale rishtedaar

Chacha: Abhi batata hun 

EXITS


5 Virat 

Labri - Kar liya duniya ka sabse jaroori kaam? Ab ye lo khaao paan kyonki team india ne jeeta hai world cup ka mukam

Khabri/Sawaalin- Kya baat hai badi tukabandi ho rahi hai?

Labri - Ab bandi to ham kisiki ban nahin paaye to socha thodi si tukbandi hi kar lete hain. Hamne siddhu ji se seekha hai, doosri line k baad jyada koi dhyaan se sunta nahin hai..

Khabri- Chalo galat bahano se sahi siddhu saab cricket ki audience to badha rahe hain…(eats paan)

Virat Kohli enters, practicing straight bowling action in air

VIRAT (to man 1): Ye khiladi chacha ka ghar kahan padega?

Man 1: falls off his chair…

Khabri: Are kya baat hai koi virat kohli ki photo laga k chala gaya (goes towards him)

Virat: (practices a straight drive to his face, almost slapping khabri)

Khabri: are mar gaye ye to asli ek dam original waala kohli hai, sir aapki chai ready h

Virat: lekin maine to order hi nahin kari

Khabri: Lekin hamne to bana di na 

Virat : ye kya hota hai? aise zabardasti koi cheez bech rahe ho..

Sawaalin : jaise aap har samay ad me bechte ki ye khalo ye peelo ye pehen lo.. bas wahin se seekha hai…


Virat - wo to Mera kaam hai

Sawaalin - to Bina baat ki chai bechna Inka kaam hai kyun sahi bola na

Virat: okay vegan chai kar do fir

Khabri: ye bakri k doodh waali hoti hai? Wo hamare paas nahin hai.

Virat: accha koi baat nahin ek kaali chai kar do

Virat sits down

Sawaalin: VIrat sir world cup jeetne ki badhai

VIrat: Thank you, thank you. (Practices pull shot in air while sitting)...sab bhagwaan ne kiya hai

Sawaalin - sir aapko final me aake man of the match Jeet k kaisa lag raha hai 

Virat - jis hisaab ki mujhe tournament ki shuruaat mili thi 76 to aaj kam hi lag raha hai. Lekin uparwaala ne sab dekh liya..


Sawaalin: accha ye bataiye ki aap itne din se Rohit sharma aur aapki ladai ki baateien media me chal rahi thi par aapne kabhi koi explanation nahin diya, kya aap unko gale lagane k liye world cup ka wait kar rahe the?...is Jeet se pehle aap Rohit se gale kyun nahin mile??

Virat: wo yaar jeet ki khushi me dekha nahin kisse gale mil Raha hun. Stadium ke Anushka bhi nahi thi.. hehe..

Sawaalin: to kyaa aapki ladai sach me chalu hai?

Virat: no comments… (hits a cover drive in air)... 

Sawaalin: Virat ji

Aap to waise rest pe rehte hain abhi achanak retirement kyun announce kar diya?  anushka ji me daanta tha k bacchon ka diaper ab tum change karoge?...

Virat: (laughs)

Sawaalin : aap Bharat k aadhe se jyada berozgaaron ko apni daadhi ki style copy karte hue dekhte hain to aapko kaisa lagta hai?

Virat: Maine bhi kisi bakri se chhapi hi thi..

Man 1:  yells Cricket GOAT 

Virat:( does a bowling action,) sab bhagwaan ka kiya hai

Sawaalin: Virat ji jay Shah ne team k liye 125 crore ka inaam ghoshit kiya hai aapko kya lagta hai ki Rinku singh k pitaji ko ab cylinder uthaana chhod dena chaahiye?

Virat: Maine bola na har cheez ki tarah ye bhi bhagwaan ne kiya hai…

Labri: Aap bhi hamaare liye ek kuch kar dijiye

Virat: Kya?

Labri: Ik baar dekh lijiye, deewana bana dijiye…deewaana nahin bana sakte to bandi bana lijiye

Virat: Mai jailor laga hun jo bandi banaunga?

Khabri: Kuch nahin sir, jai shah ne jo jeetne ki khushi me 125 karore announce kiya hai uske peeche hai
Virat: Mai bhi usi k peeche yahan aaya hun...Abhi ye bataiye khiladi chacha ka Ghar kahan hai

Sawaalin : udhar

/extra 

